// to focus on the desired screen and scroll the page
document.querySelector("#main-content").scrollBy(0,700)

here document will focus on the entire screen
querySelector use for which query we want
inside it give the location where we want to focus by giving the locator and then scroll it.

example
 \
 JavaScriptExecutor js = (javaScriptExecutor)driver;
 js.executeScript(document.querySelector("#main-content").scrollBy(0,700));